{"2872110": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Superdeluxe", "steam_appid": 2872110, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SUPERDELUXE! is a visual novel where you play as a young trans woman, Join their adventures of romancing other girls and helping them to find their true identities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has episodic stories about many trans girls and their sex lives! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872110/extras/0fb99a5e217af46a3ed598be7916e72f.webp?t=1775314997\" width=640 height=50 /></span>A Slice-of-Life LGBTQ+ Experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live through the straightforward stories of Our Protagonist and her Friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn Anime Art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every character in the game has been hand-drawn </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Episodic Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each episode focuses on one love character in the game, but beware there are some choices you have to make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2872110/extras/254601cdf35adcb98132c93b1cc5f4e0.webp?t=1775314997\" width=640 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 (and counting) episodes to unlock! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 28000 words of dialogue!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 90 to 120 minutes of playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple straightforward stories. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ct